ly this cron session is active (no other sessions), send HEARTBEAT_OK only.\\nIf there are no sessions at all, stay SILENT.\\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 15th, 2026 - 12:54 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-15 00:54 UTC\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776214507530,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"0c211062\",\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Let me check the sessions_list to see what active master-orchestrator sessions are running.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_onvvs709b2oh_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"kinds\": [\n                  \"agent\"\n                ],\n                \"limit\": 20,\n                \"messageLimit\": 3\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 345,\n            \"output\": 69,\n            \"totalTokens\": 14263,\n            \"cacheRead\": 10789,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 3060,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776214507684,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e14ec2e0881b7f57b066f119d9793\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"ba0fb787\",\n            \"seq\": 2\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"heartbeat\"\n      },\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report\",\n      \"di